text: Saw V is a 2008 American horror movie directed by David Hackl and written by Patrick Melton and Marcus Dunstan. It stars Tobin Bell, Costas Mandylor, Scott Patterson, Betsy Russell, Mark Rolston, Julie Benz, Carlo Rota, and Meagan Good. It is the fifth installment in the Saw franchise, and was released in North America on October 24, 2008. ==References== Category:2008 horror movies Category:Saw movies Category:Lionsgate movies
